longBusinessSummary: Molecule Holdings Inc. engages in production and co-packing of cannabis-infused beverages in Canada. It also offers cannabis extracts, beverages, edibles, and topical products directly to provincial retailers. The company offers its beverage products under the PHRESH, KLÕN, EMBODY, and CANAJO brands. Molecule Holdings Inc. is based in Lansdowne, Canada.
